ZH: 请告诉我您的住所。
EN: Please tell me your address.

ZH: 这个信封上没有写收件人的住所。
EN: There is no recipient's address written on this envelope.

ZH: 你知道他的住所吗？
EN: Do you know his address?

ZH: 明天我要去邮局更改我的住所。
EN: I will go to the post office tomorrow to change my address.

ZH: 我常常会忘记我的住所。
EN: I often forget my address.

ZH: 他寄给我一个包裹，但是没写我的住所。
EN: He sent me a package, but didn't write my address.

ZH: 请在邮件上写明您的住所。
EN: Please indicate your address on the mail.

ZH: 我的一个朋友刚刚搬到一个新的住所。
EN: One of my friends just moved to a new address.

ZH: 这个住所非常适合居住。
EN: This address is very suitable for living.

ZH: 我搬家后要更改我的住所。
EN: I need to change my address after moving.

ZH: 他从邮局寄了一封信到我住所。
EN: He sent a letter to my address from the post office.

ZH: 我已经提交了我的新住所给邮局。
EN: I have submitted my new address to the post office.

ZH: 这是我新买的房子的住所。
EN: This is the address of my newly bought house.

ZH: 请用红笔在表格上标明您的住所。
EN: Please mark your address on the form with a red pen.

ZH: 我从朋友那里得到了她的住所。
EN: I got her address from a friend.

ZH: 你能给我一个准确的住所吗？
EN: Can you give me an accurate address?

ZH: 请将我的住所更改为新的地址。
EN: Please change my address to the new one.

ZH: 请给我一个附近的住所。
EN: Please give me a nearby address.

ZH: 那个公司的住所在城市中心。
EN: The company's address is in the city center.

ZH: 我迷路了，不记得我的住所了。
EN: I got lost and don't remember my address.
